c74object.description:
abc.hoa.optim~ is an High Order Ambisonics (HOA) optimization process. This objects enable to apply optimizations to the sound field with 3 levels (depending on optimtype value). It provides solutions when having an audience that cannot be considered as staying in the center of the ambisonic circle.


      -basic (0) has no effect;

      -maxRe (1) optimization is used when the audience is confined to the center of the circle;

      -inPhase (2) optimization is used when the audience covers all the circle.
